(100199, 'Serge', 'NTAMACK', 'Mr', '', '30', 'cm', '', '', '', 'Directeur juridique de Microsoft EMEA et VC', 'I am an Attorney & Policy Practionner who is passionate about the new challenges that are at the intersection of technology, business and policy issues. I am excited about improving the society and helping Governments in Africa to deliver world class services to their citizens.\r\n\r\nIn my current role, I design and lead execution of a range of Regulatory Affairs and Public Policy Programs accross Middle East and Africa.\r\nAreas of Experience:\r\n** Innovation (Incubators, Business Angels, Start Up) \r\n** Public sector transformation, Digital agendas\r\n** Cloud Computing policy issues such as Data Privacy, including GDPR compliance, Cybersecurity and Transparency\r\n** Policy and Regulatory issues around Artificial Intelligence, Internet of Things, Machine Learning\r\n** Government affairs, regulatory strategies and policy formation\r\n** Intellectual property compliance\r\n** Industry coalitions, Trade Policy\r\n** Commercial Law (OHADA), Cloud contracts\r\n** \"Closing the gap\" - Focused on building relations between private companies, NGOs, citizens and Public Institutions.', 16, 2, 1, 1);
