(100102, 'Bechir', 'OMRAN', 'Mr', '', '30', 'tn', '', '20870840', 'Bechir@chachia.me', 'Chachia Inc', 'A Business Development professional specialized in formulating and growing strategic partnerships that thrive on innovation in the creative and digital media industry. Bechir co-founded and been a key part of several successful start-ups including a big data and machine learning technology firm out of Beirut, Kharabeesh a platform for Digital Creators and a modern media curating and producing dynamic content, CHBK Network, and currently leading Chachia Inc one of the very few content distribution, digital rights management and copyright protection ventures launched out of the Maghreb region.', 1, 2, 1, 1),
